OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with spells of rain.
OL,7,FRemaining cloudy overnight with
OL,8,Ffurther rain, perhaps easing across
OL,9,FOrkney later. Fresh to strong
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA cloudy day with spells of
OL,13,Frain or drizzle, perhaps turning more
OL,14,Fpersistent for a time in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Less windy.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FBrighter on Thursday with showers
OL,19,Flikely later. Bright with showers on
OL,20,FFriday, windy later. Drier on Saturday.
